title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Merryweather Security Livery for the DH-7 Iron Mule
content: Successfully completing The Titan Job from Oscar Guzman Flies Again anytime through May 21 will reward you with the limited-time Merryweather Security livery for the Buckingham DH-7 Iron Mule (Helicopter), delivered within 72 hours of completion.
